The ams_module is required for XtreemOS installations to allow grid users to access their home volumes.

1. build the shared library
> python scons.py

2. create the policies directory
> mkdir -p /lib/xtreemfs/policies/

3. copy the .so file
> cp lib/libxos_ams_flog.so /lib/xtreemfs/policies/


The client (xtsf_mount) will automatically load the library and use the AMS for account mappings.
